videos.headline: Zamir White scores on Georgia's opening drive
videos.description: Georgia RB Zamir White rushes through traffic and into the end zone for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Zamir White scores on Georgia's opening drive) 2021/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kendall Milton powers it in for another Georgia TD
videos.description: Georgia RB Kendall Milton pushes through a pile and across the goal line for the score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kendall Milton powers it in for another Georgia TD) 2021/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia fans erupt after a blocked punt turns into a TD
videos.description: Dan Jackson blocks the punt for Georgia and Zamir White recovers it for a touchdown, making the Bulldogs' fans go wild.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia fans erupt after a blocked punt turns into a TD) 2021/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zamir White's third TD overall piles it on for Georgia
videos.description: Georgia RB Zamir White rushes 15 yards for a touchdown, increasing the Bulldogs' lead to 34-0 over Arkansas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Zamir White's third TD overall piles it on for Georgia) 2021/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia steamrolls Arkansas in top-10 matchup
videos.description: Zamir White and the No. 2 Georgia Bulldogs crush the No. 8 Arkansas Razorbacks 37-0 on Saturday.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Georgia steamrolls Arkansas in top-10 matchup) 2021/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trust, patience key for Dawgs in rout of Hogs
videos.description: Following the shutout victory against No. 8 Arkansas, No. 2 Georgia LB Nakobe Dean explains the Dawgs' mentality heading into the week.

videos.headline: No. 2 Georgia jumps on No. 8 Arkansas early, often
videos.description: The Bulldogs go up by three touchdowns in the first quarter and cruise to a 37-0 victory over the Razorbacks in the showdown of unbeatens.
